{"id": "9fdb200d-2432-4ebe-ace9-c38deb577843", "task_id": "454526c8-cf1d-4e5a-9e90-46aa41eed358", "path": "templates/index.html", "artifact_type": "file", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>CYBERNETIC LOGIN // ACCESS PROTOCOL</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oxanium:wght@300;400;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --dark-bg: #1a0f2c;\n            --main-text-color: #00ffcc;\n            --secondary-text-color: #8c8c8c;\n            --accent-color: #ff33cc;\n            --border-color: #0088ff;\n            --input-bg: #2a1f42;\n            --button-bg: #00ffcc;\n            --button-text: #1a0f2c;\n            --glow-filter: drop-shadow(0 0 5px var(--accent-color)) drop-shadow(0 0 10px var(--accent-color));\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Oxanium', sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--dark-bg);\n            color: var(--main-text-color);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        body::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-image: \n                repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0,255,204,0.05) 0px, rgba(0,255,204,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 50px),\n                repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,255,204,0.05) 0px, rgba(0,255,204,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 50px);\n            opacity: 0.1;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .login-container {\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            padding: 40px 60px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: \n                0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.5),\n                0 0 40px rgba(255, 51, 204, 0.3);\n            text-align: center;\n            max-width: 400px;\n            width: 90%;\n            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n            animation: glitchEffect 10s infinite alternate;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitchEffect {\n            0% { transform: translate(0); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.5), 0 0 40px rgba(255, 51, 204, 0.3); }\n            2% { transform: translate(-2px, -2px); box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.6), 0 0 30px rgba(255, 51, 204, 0.4); }\n            4% { transform: translate(2px, 2px); box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.4), 0 0 50px rgba(255, 51, 204, 0.2); }\n            6% { transform: translate(0); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.5), 0 0 40px rgba(255, 51, 204, 0.3); }\n            8% { transform: translate(-1px, 1px); }\n            10% { transform: translate(1px, -1px); }\n            12% { transform: translate(0); }\n            100% { transform: translate(0); }\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;\n            color: var(--main-text-color);\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--main-text-color), 0 0 10px var(--main-text-color);\n            filter: var(--glow-filter);\n        }\n\n        .input-group {\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            text-align: left;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;\n        }\n\n        input[type=\"text\"],\n        input[type=\"password\"] {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: var(--input-bg);\n            color: var(--main-text-color);\n            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 0 5px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        input[type=\"text\"]:focus,\n        input[type=\"password\"]:focus {\n            border-color: var(--accent-color);\n            outline: none;\n            box-shadow: \n                0 0 0 2px var(--accent-color),\n                inset 0 0 8px rgba(255, 51, 204, 0.5);\n            filter: var(--glow-filter);\n        }\n\n        button {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background-color: var(--button-bg);\n            color: var(--button-text);\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            filter: var(--glow-filter);\n            font-family: 'Oxanium', sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--main-text-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--accent-color);\n            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 5px var(--accent-color)) drop_shadow(0 0 15px var(--accent-color));\n        }\n\n        button:active {\n            transform: translateY(2px);\n        }\n\n        .error-message {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;\n            font-size: 0.85em;\n            margin-top: -10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"login-container\">\n        <h1>CYBERNETIC LOGIN</h1>\n        <form action=\"/login\" method=\"POST\">\n            <div class=\"input-group\">\n                <label for=\"username\">[[ USERNAME ]]</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"username\" name=\"username\" required autofocus>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"input-group\">\n                <label for=\"password\">[[ PASSWORD ]]</label>\n                <input type=\"password\" id=\"password\" name=\"password\" required>\n            </div>\n            {% if error %}\n                <p class=\"error-message\">{{ error }}</p>\n            {% endif %}\n            <button type=\"submit\">ACCESS SYSTEM //></button>\n        </form>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n", "patches": [], "metadata": {"language": "html", "framework": "static_html", "explanation": "This HTML file creates a cyberpunk-themed login page. It includes:\n- A basic HTML5 structure with `meta` tags for character set and viewport.\n- Two Google Fonts ('Oxanium' and 'Share Tech Mono') for a futuristic look.\n- Embedded CSS providing a dark background, neon-like text colors, glowing effects, and subtle glitch animations on the login container and input fields. CSS variables are used for easy theme customization.\n- A `div` with class `login-container` to house the login form, styled with dark transparency, neon borders, and a shadow.\n- An `<h1>` title styled with a monospace font and text shadows to enhance the cyberpunk feel.\n- A `<form>` element configured with `action=\"/login\"` and `method=\"POST\"` for proper submission to a backend. This adheres to the critical requirement of not using `event.preventDefault()`.\n- Two `input` fields (`username` and `password`) with corresponding `label` elements within `input-group` divs for structural styling.\n- A `button` with `type=\"submit\"` for form submission, styled with hover and active effects.\n- A Jinja2 template block `{% if error %}` to display an error message, assuming the backend might pass an `error` variable to the template.", "dependencies": []}, "created_at": "2026-05-17 15:52:59.190934"}